description.value: Starmaker is a decentralized fundraising platform and exchange that empowers Web3 projects to raise funds and facilitate trading. Operating on zkSync and Mantle networks, it offers a secure environment for token swaps and liquidity provision. The platform's native token, STAR, is used for governance and utility within the ecosystem.

description: zkSync is a Layer 2 scaling solution for Ethereum that utilizes zero-knowledge rollups (ZK-rollups) to enhance transaction throughput while maintaining security, decentralization, and privacy. It provides institutional-grade security with user-level privacy using selective disclosure and onchain cryptographic proofs. Individual transaction details remain hidden within ZK proofs, offering superior privacy compared to Optimistic Rollups. zkSync achieves low costs (~$0.0001/transfer) with real-time UX through Airbender high-frequency proving.
